item.title: I don't know what to do? WHAT IS WRONG!
item.dc:creator: @n0va_k0 n0va k0
item.description:
@n0va_k0 wrote:

Almost everyone here has no idea because they don’t have a router. If you have a router(wireless) you can’t portforward on that computer. If your dad or mom or anyone else in the house has a laptop or w\e, you have to portforward on that one because they don’t have a router. If you don’t have a router then you don’t need portforward and can make a server right off the bat.
